2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the performance of LDPC codes in a communication system, which is relevant to networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper may be relevant to the study of error correction in social and information networks.
